name: 1,4-benzenedicarhoxylic acid polymer with 1,4-cyclohexanedimethanol and 1,2-ethanediol

No. 25038-91-9), with 1,4-cyclohexanedimethanol(consisting of 70 percent trans isomer and 30 percent cis isomer) representing 35 to 80 mole percent of the diol units and 1,2-ethanediol representing 65 to 20 mole percent of the diol units.
